Installation Instructions
*************************

Relies on VESmail -
git@github.com:vesvault/VESmail.git

Put the VESmail-apple dir in VESmail/app dir (VESmail/app/VESmail-apple),
or adjust the paths in libvesmail/

libcrypto.a and libssl.a have to be built for each target (OpenSSL).

libcurl.a has to be built for each target (cURL).

libVES.a has to be built for each target -
git@github.com:vesvault/libVES.c.git

Use libvesmail/make-* to build libvesmail.a for each target.

Download snif-tunl for iOS VPN -
git@github.com:vesvault/snif-tunl.git
Use libsnifl/make-* to build libsnifl.a

Use XCode to build the solution for each target - macOS and iOS-vpn
